  Tng Na2-a e5 si5, toa7 chui2 biat8 se3-kan, hit si5 lang5 sou2 tiam3 e5 toe7-ui7 chi2 u7 nng7 khoan2. (1) Chun5-lai7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 lang5. (2) Chun5-goa7 hou7 chui2 im-si2 e5 lang5. I2-goa7 bo5 sou2-chai7 thang hou7 hit si5 e5 lang5 tiam3. Ia5-sou siat phi3-ju7 kong2, tho2 hi5 e5 lang5 pha-tioh8 hi5, ¡§Keng2 ho2--e5 he7 loh8 khah-a2, phaiN2--e5 hiat-kak8 khi3.¡¨ Koh kong2, ¡§Chap8 e5 chai7-sek-lu2 ngia5-chih sin kiaN2-sai3, chit8 poaN3 gong7--e5, chit8 poaN3 gau5--e5. Gau5--e5 hou7 chu2-lang5 chiap-lap8 jip8 chhu3, gong7--e5 ku7-choat8 ti7 goa7-bin7 boe7 tit jip8.¡¨ Tai7-khai3 chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 e5 i3-su3. Seng3-keng put-chi2 choe7 sou2-chai7 u7 kong2-khi2, long2-chong2 si7 phi3-ju7 se3-kan lang5 sou2 tiam3 e5 toe7-ui7 chi2 u7 nng7 khoan2. (1) Thian-tong5. (2) Te7-gek8. I2-goa7 bo5 te7 saN khoan2 e5 toe7-ui7 thang tiam3. 
  1. Thian-tong5. (Khe2-si7-liok8 7:13-16[15].) Hiah-e5 chheng7 peh8-saN--e5, chiu7-si7 tui3 keng-ke3 toa7 hoan7-lan7, bat eng7 IuN5-ko e5 huih soe2 i e5 la5-sam5, sou2-i2 tit-tioh8 tiam3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5. 
  2. Te7-gek8. (Khe2-si7-liok8 6:15,16.) Se3-kan chiah-e5 ong5, koaN-oan5, ho2-giah8 e5 lang5, iong2-beng2 e5 lang5, chu2-lang5, lou5-pok8, long2-chong2 bih ti7 soaN-khang--nih8, toa7 siaN kio3 kong2, ¡§SoaN ah! Tioh8 pang-loh8-lai5 kham3--goa2, hou7 goa2 bih ti7 lai7-bin7, thang siam2-pi7 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 siu7-khi3.¡¨ 
  Kang ChiN5 Kap SiuN2-su3 e5 Hun-piat8.
  Kang-chiN5 si7 choe3 kang lang5 eng-kai tit-tioh8 e5 hun7-giah8. SiuN2-su3 si7 chu2-lang5 ti7 hun7-giah8 i2-goa7 tek8-piat8 siuN2-su3--e5. Se3-kan lang5 bo5 chit8 e5 bo5 ke3-sit, sou2-i2 Seng3-keng kong2, ¡§Choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5 si7 si2-bo5.¡¨ Chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-su3 si7 eng2-oah8, lang5 na7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, chhim-sin3 Ia5-sou chiu7 oe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 un-su3. In-ui7 choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5 Ia5-sou pun2-sin i2-keng thoe3 lan2 heng5, lau5 huih, pang3-sak sin-khu thoe3 choe7-jin5 si2, chit-e5 si7 te7 it kui3-khi3 e5 kang-chiN5. 
  U7 Mia5 Bo5 Sit8 e5 Gui5-hiam2.
  Bat u7 lang5 khi2-thau5 him-bou7 to7-li2, bo5 loa7 ku2 nia2 soe2-le2 jip8 kau3-hoe7, soa3 tam-tng chip-su7, tiuN2-lo2 i2-kip8 thoan5-to7 e5 chit, eng7 Seng3-keng e5 to7-li2 mng7--i, i chin gau5 in3, u7 si5 tu2-tioh8 oh e5 toe5-bak8, i iah8 pian7-lun7 put-chi2 thau3-thiat beng5-pek8, goa7-iong5 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 chin thang chun-tiong7, siong-sek8 e5 lang5 o-lo2 i choe3 kau3-hoe7 e5 thiau7-chioh8. 
  An2-ni chiau3 goa7-mau7 khoaN3 si7 kek8 ki5 tui3-tiong7 to7-li2, ui7-tioh8 kau3-hoe7 jiat8-sim chhut-lat8, chong2-si7 soe3-ji7 ka7 i chha5-kho2, i e5 sim oan5-choan5 bo5 hap8 Ki-tok saN-lian5. Ki-tok kong2, ¡§Kio3 goa2 choe3 Chu2--e5, bo5 tek-khak tak8 e5 jip8 Thian-kok, tok8-tok8 chun-than3 ThiN-pe7 e5 chi2-i3 e5 lang5 oe7 jip8.¡§ ¡§Tng sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5, tek-khak u7 lang5 kong2, goa2 kiam2 m7 si7 hong7 Kiu3 Chu2 e5 mia5 thoan5-to7 koaN2-kui2, kiaN5 tak8 hang7 ki5-koai3 e5 tai7-chi3 kap sin5-jiah--mah? Chu2 siaN2-su7 m7-jin7 goa2?¡¨ Goa2 tek-khak in3 kong2, ¡§Lin2 long2 si7 choe3 phaiN2 e5 lang5, tioh8 kin2-kin2 khi3, goa2 m7-bat lin2.¡¨ TaN Kau3-hoe7 lai7 u7 lang5, chhui3 chheng-hou Kiu3 Chu2, sim-lai7 bo5 kap Kiu3 Chu2 saN-lian5, sou2 kong2 sou2 kiaN5 bo5 kap seng3-to7 saN-hap8, chit ho7 lang5 thai2-tho2 u7 thang ng3-bang7 jip8 Thian-kok, bian2-tit te7-gek8 e5 heng5-hoat8. Sit8-chai7 chin gui5-hiam2. 
  ThiN-e7 Kan u7 Chit Ho7 Pan7-gi5 Su7--Mah? 
  Chit8 e5 bok8-su khia7-khi2 oa2-kun7 thou5-thoaN3 khong3. Tak8 pai2 kau3 chiah8 jit8-tau3 e5 si5, i chiu7 jip8 khong3-lai7 thoan5 Hok-im hou7 choe3 kang lang5 thiaN. Jip8 khong3 e5 khang khoan2-sit chhin-chhiuN7 chiN2, tui3 teng2-bin7 kau3 khong3-toe2, u7 pah goa7 tng7 chhim. Chu2-lang5 u7 pi7-pan7 ki-khi3, oe7 chiuN7 oe7 loh8, thang chiuN7 thou5-thoaN3 chhut khong3, bian2 eng7 lang5 e5 lat8, put-chi2 li7-pian7. Khong3-lai7 sou2-chai7 put-chi2 khui-khoah, oe7 iong5-un2 kang2 chheng lang5 ti7 lai7-bin7 ong2-lai5 choe3-kang. 
  Chit8 jit8 bok8-su loh8 khong3-lai7, long2-chong2 e5 choe3 kang lang5 tu2 teh chiah8 jit8-tau3, chiu7 seng7 ki-hoe7 kong2 to7-li2, kong2, ¡§Se3-kan lang5 tak8 e5 u7 tek choe7 thiN, kai-chai3 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok thoe3 lang5 si2 siok8 choe7, chiah u7 thang lau5 kau3 kin-a2-jit8 bian2 si2, lan2 lang5 na7 kheng2 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, chiu7 khoai3-khoai3 thang thoat-li7 te7-gek8, lai5 chiuN7 kau3 Thian-kok.¡¨ 
  Bo5 loa7 ku2, choe3 kang lang5 chiah8 pa2, u7 chit8 e5 thau5-bak8 ka7 bok8-su kong2: ¡§Li2 kong2 lang5 na7 kheng2 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, chiu7 khoai3-khoai3 thang chiuN7 kau3 Thian-kok. He kau3 hiah khoai3 kong2, kiam2 thiN-e7 kan u7 chit ho7 pan7-gi5 su7--mah?¡¨ Nng7 lang5 na2 kiaN5 na2 kong2, chha-put-to kau3 chhut khong3 e5 sou2-chai7, bok8-su kiah8-thau5 khoaN3, tui3 khong3-toe2 kau3 teng2-bin7, sit8-chai7 put chi2 koaiN5, chiu7 mng7 thau5-bak8 kong2, ¡§Tui3 chia kau3 toe7-bin7 loa7 koaiN5?¡¨ In3 kong2, ¡§Chit8-pah poeh-chap8 tng7.¡¨ Bok8-su kong2, ¡§Khong3-lai7 tak8 bin7 e5 piah long2 bo5 kia7-a2, thai2-tho2 oe7 khi2--khi3?¡¨ In3 kong2, ¡§Bok8-su ah, li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 toe7-bin7 e5 ki-khi3, u7 tiau3 chit8 e5 chiuN7-loh8 e5 khi3-ku7 ti7-teh--mah? Lang5 beh khi2, a2-si7 beh loh8, na7 jip8 chit-e5 khi3-ku7, bo5 chit8 bak8-nih ku2 liam5-piN kau3 te3.¡¨ Bok8-su ke2-i3 kong2, ¡§He kau3 hiah iong5-iN7, piN5-toe7 to7 tioh8 kiaN5 ku2-ku2, ho5-hong3 chit-e5 beh khi2--khi3 tioh8 eng7 chiuN7--e5, li2 chiah kong2 bian2 chit8 bak8-nih ku2 chiu7 kau3 te3, kiam2 thiN-e7 kan u7 chit ho7 pan7-gi5 su7--mah?¡¨ Thau5-bak8 kong2, ¡§Bo5, thau5-ke hui3 loa7 choe7 khou2-sim, khai loa7 choe7 chiN5-gun5, pi7-pan7 chit-e5 khi3-ku7, chiah u7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 li7-pian7. Bok8-su, li2 khoaN3 khi3-ku7 chit8 chiuN7 chit8 loh8, put-ko3 tiap8 a2 ku2 na7-tiaN7--houN7. Che long2 si7 thau5-ke keng-eng5 kui2-na7 chap8 ni5, sou2 khai-siau m7 si7 sio2-khoa2, li2 kiam2 bo5 khoaN3--kiN3?¡¨ Bok8-su in3 kong2, ¡§Tioh8 lah, lang5 chiuN7 kau3 Thian-kok iah8 m7 si7 khoai3 e5 su7, si7 tui3 ThiN pe7 ti7 kang2-chheng pah ni5 cheng5, tiau-ti5 chhe I tok8-siN e5 Seng3 KiaN2, lim5-kau3 se3-kan, thoe3 li2 goa2 siok8 choe7, sou2 khai-siau kap chit-e5 saN pi2, m7 na7 ek, ban7, tiau7 e5 pe7-sou3, lan2 iah8 long2 m7 chai hiah pan7-gi5.¡¨ 
  Cheng3 choe3 kang lang5 thiaN-kiN3 bok8-su sou2 kong2--e5, long2 siu7 kam2-tong7, choe3 chit8 jit8 kui Chu2--e5 kui2-na7 chheng lang5, thau5-bak8 koh khah jiat8-sim. 
  Chiu-ui5 Si7 Ho2 Chui2, Gong7 Lang5 Chhui3 Ta Si2. 
  Lam5 Bi2-chiu e5 pak-bin7, u7 chit8 tiau5 toa7 kang mia5 A-ma2-sun3, chui2 put chheng oe7 lim--tit. Kang-khau2 ng3 lam5 jip8 toa7 sai-iuN5, si3 bin7 bo5 soaN bo5 su7, chui2 chhin-chhiuN7 kap thiN saN-chiap. 
  Cha2-jit8 u7 chit8 chiah chun5 tui3 Au-chiu lai5, hoan7-tioh8 hong-thai, chun5 sai2 boe7 chin3 thang jip8 kang-lai7. Ian5-chhian5 ku2-ku2, chun5-lai7 sou2 chek-chu7 e5 chiaN2 chui2, long2 liau2. Hit si5 tu2-tu2 si7 joah8-thiN, chun5 lai7 e5 lang5-kheh chin chhui3-ta, siuN7-ai3 chiuN7 hai2-chui2 khi2-lai5 lim, u7 e5 chou2-tong3 kong2, ¡§Hai2-chui2 kiam5, lim liau2 oe7 na2 chhui3-ta, sui-jian5 lim e5 si5 chhin-chhiuN7 li5-a2 oe7 tam5 au5, bo5 loa7 ku2 sin-khu koh khah joah8, chhui3 koh khah ta, lou7-be2 tek-khak hun7-khi3 lai5 si2.¡¨ Lang5-kheh chiu7 m7-kaN2 choe3. Koh tiap8-a2 ku2, chhui3-ta tong3-boe7-tiau5, sin-khu hui-siong5 kan-khou2, chha-put-to beh si2. Gui5-kip e5 tiong-kan hut-jian5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 chiah phang5-chun5 tui3 hng7-hng7 lai5, tai7-ke hoaN-hi2 kiu3 chhiN kau3--lah. Chiu7 seng ki5 kiu5 kiu3, ki5 sou2 chhut e5 ki3-ho7 si7 ¡§Bo5 chui2,¡¨ ¡§Khoah--si2,¡¨ ¡§Kiu5 chan7¡¨ chi2 lak8 ji7. Lai5 e5 chun5 khoaN3--kiN3 iah8 seng-ki5 chhut ki3-ho7 in3, ¡§Chun5 goa7,¡¨ ¡§Chui2 chiaN2,¡¨ ¡§Thang lim.¡¨ Cheng3 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 liau2 put-chi2 gong5-ngiah8, in-ui7 chun5 i2-keng kau3 A-ma2-sun3 kang-khau2, sui-jian5 si3-bin7 bo5 soaN bo5 su7, sit8-chai7 chun5 sai2 jip8 chiaN2-chui2 e5 kai3 lai7 ia7 m7 chai. Chiu7 tak8 e5 ka-ki7 chek-pi7 kong2, ¡§Kiu3 chhiN ti7 bak8-cheng5, lan2 lai5 chhui3-ta--si2, kiam2 bo5 chin gong7.¡¨ 
  Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2 chu5-pi moa2-moa2, se3-kan lang5 tiam3 ti7 hit tiong-kan, bo5 chit8 lang5 oe7 chai, hoan2-tng2 chhe7 pat8 e5 chin2-kiu3 e5 hoat-tou7, tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 chun5--nih8 chhui3-ta e5 lang5 chit8 iuN7. TaN ai3 khou2-khng3 tai7-ke, lan2 e5 si3-bin7 long2 si7 Chu2 e5 un-tian2, na7 kheng2 hoaN-hi2 seng5-siu7 chiu7 thang tit--tioh8. Seng3-keng kong2, ¡§KiN3-na7 ki5-to2 Chu2 e5 mia5--e5, tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3.¡¨ 
  Goa2 Tok8-it e5 Kiu3 Chu2. 
  Goa2 ng3-bang7 choe7 sia3-bian2 lai5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, chi2-u7 sin3 Ki-tok choe3 goa2 tok8-it e5 Kiu3 Chu2 na7-tiaN7. 
  Tok8-it Kiu3 Chu2 e5 i3-su3, chiu7-si7 goa2 sin3 a2-bo5, kap pat8 lang5 bo5 kan-siap8. Kui-oa2 Ki-tok Ia5-sou, chiu7 ban7-tai7 e5 hok-khi3, tok8-tok8 goa2 hiong2-siu7, na7 bo5, chiu7 eng2-oan2 e5 kan-khou2, iah8 si7 goa2 ka-ki7 tam-tng. Sou2-i2 Tai7-pit8 e5 si (Si-phian 23 phiN) kong2, ¡§Chu2 si7 goa2 e5 bok8-chia2.¡¨ Chiu7-si7 chit ho7 i3-su3. Chong2 lai5 kong2, Ki-tok chhut-si3 ui7-tioh8 ka3-si7--goa2, si7 ui7-tioh8 chin2-kiu3--goa2, sou2-i2 goa2 kui-oa2 sin3-than3 e5 sim, tioh8 tui3 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 sim-lai7 chhut, m7 si7 pat8 lang5 sou2 oe7 thang ka7 goa2 thoe3. 
  He2-chhia SaN-lian5 e5 Kau. 
  He2-chhia teh kiaN5, saN-khan saN-thoa poaN3 li2 goa7 tng5, u7 e5 kui2 chap8 tiuN, poaN5 nia2 chhng soaN, long2 put-chi2 un2-tang3. In-ui7 ti7 tak8 tiuN chhia e5 cheng5-au7 u7 kau-a2 thang saN-kau. Kau-a2 m7 si7 sui2, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 thau5 ji7 teng2 chhia-lai7 khi3-ku7 hiah ho2 khoaN3, mih8-kiaN7 hiah chiau5-pi7, iau2-ku2 ti7 beh khui chhia e5 tai7-seng, koan2 chhia--e5, tioh8 kau3 tak8 tiuN soe3-ji7 sun5-si7 tak8 e5 kau-a2 u7 ho2-se3 saN-kau a2-bo5, siat-su2 bo5 saN-kau saN-lian5, tek-khak boe7 thang thoa kau3 sou2 ai3 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7. 
  Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 kin2-sin7 i e5 kiaN5 choe3, chun2-chat ka-ki7 e5 su-iok8, an2-ni thang kong2 bo5 bak-tioh8 se3-kan sou2 u7 e5 phaiN2. Kiam2-chhai2 chit ho7 lang5 iah8 u7 nia2 soe2-le2 than3 to7-li2, khak-siu2 Kau3-hoe7 e5 kui-ku2 le2-gi5, sou2 kong2 sou2 kiaN5, bo5 chit8 tiam2-a2 thang hiam5, an2-ni chiau3 khoaN3, thang kong2 i si7 chit8 e5 ho2 lang5, m7 ku2 boe7 tit thang phah-sng3 oa2-kho3 chiah-e5 chiu7 chiuN7 Thian-kok kap Siong7-te3 choe3 tui. In-ui7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok phi3-ju7 chhin-chhiuN7 chhia-thau5, long2-chong2 e5 sin3-tou5 chhin-chhiuN7 chhia, sin3-tou5 e5 phin2-heng7 sui-jian5 toan-chiaN3, siat-su2 sim bo5 kap Kiu3 Chu2 saN-lian5, iah8 boe7 thang kau3 hok-khi3 khoai3-lok8 e5 sou2-chai7. Sou2-i2 Ia5-sou kong2, ¡§Goa2 si7 phu5-to5-chhiu7, lin2 long2 si7 ki-oaiN7, ki siN ti7 chhiu7-sin chiu7 oe7 am7, li7-khui oe7 ta.¡¨ Tu2-tu2 si7 chit ho7 i3-su3. 
  Koh lun7 sin3 e5 sim si7 choe3 lan2 lang5 kap Kiu3 Chu2 saN-lian5 e5 kau, Ki-tok kong2, ¡§ThiaN-kiN3 goa2 sou2 thoan5 e5 to7-li2, koh sin3 chhe goa2 lai5 e5 ThiN Pe7-e5, hit lang5 tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3.¡¨ Sou2-i2 u7 toa7 sin3 sim kap Kiu3 Chu2 saN-lian5, chiu7 kiaN5 thiN-lou7 tek-khak chin kin2, pi2 he2-chhia teh kiaN5 koh khah kin2. Na7 bo5 lian5 ti7 Kiu3 Chu2, sui-jian5 kin2-sin7 kiaN5 choe3, un-khun5 pai3-kui7, bo5 Tek-khak oe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 hoaN-hi2 chiap-lap8. 
  Siong5-siong5 khoaN3-kiN3 he2-chhia kiaN5 kau3 poaN3 lou7 iah8 u7 pang3 tng7--e5, tok8-tok8 Ki-tok tui3 ti7 hak8-seng si7 si5-si5 saN thiaN3 saN lian5, bo5 chit8 si5 pang3-sak, siat-su2 lang5 bo5 ka-ki7 pang3-sak, chhin-chhiuN7 chhia e5 kau-a2 ka-ki7 tng7, chiu7 tek-khak boe7 poaN3 lou7 theng5--khi3. Seng3-keng Iok-han7 10:28 ki3-chai3 Ki-tok e5 oe7, kong2, ¡§Sin3 Goa2 e5 lang5, Goa2 siuN2-su3 i eng2-oah8. eng2 boe7 tim5-lun5, bo5 lang5 oe7 tui3 Goa2 e5 chhiu2 chhiuN2--khi3.¡¨ Che si7 beng5 e5 kan-cheng3.  
  U7 chit8 e5 thak8 chheh lang5 chhau3-kham2 hian Seng3-keng teh thak8, thong jit8 thong mi5 long2 m7 kam pang3 chhiu2. Hut-jian5 i e5 bou2 hian mng5-li5 jip8, thak8 chheh lang5 tai3 iu-iong5 ka7 i e5 bou2 kong2, ¡§Chiau3 Seng3-keng sou2 kong2, chiu7 lan2 sou2 choe3 boe7 bian2 tit jip8 m7 tioh8 e5 lou7¡¨. Koh thak8 kui2-na7 jit8, koh ka7 i e5 bou2 kong2, ¡§Chham2 lah, chiau3 Seng3-keng e5 oe7, chin li2 goa2 tioh8 eng2-oan2 tim5-lun5, bo5 koh oah8 e5 ng3-bang7.¡¨ Koh thak8 kui2-na7 jit8, Sin-iok thong pun2 long2-chong2 khoaN3 liau2, chiu7 pang3 Seng3-keng, hoaN-hi2 ka7 i e5 bou2 kong2, ¡§Kai-chai3 u7 Ki-tok thoe3 lan2 si2. TaN ti7 si2 e5 tiong-kan u7 oah8 e5 ng3-bang7--lah, tok8-tok8 tioh8 seng5-sim sin3-than3, kap Ki-Tok saN-lian5, chiu7 thang tit--tioh8. Cha2 lan2 ka-ki7 phah-sng3 kin2-sin7 kiaN5-choe3, ng3-bang7 oh8 choe3 ho2 lang5, tak8 hang7 bo5 chho3-gou7, bo5 phah-sng3 ka-ki7 liah8 choe3 tioh8--e5 tu2-tu2 si7 m7 tioh8, che chiu7-si7 jip8 ti7 m7 tioh8 e5 lou7. TaN thak8 Seng3-keng, chiah chai Siong7-te3 e5 Seng3, chheng-khi3, lang5 sou2 pi2 boe7 oe7 tioh8, tui3 cha2 kau3 taN bo5 chit8 lang5 oan5-choan5 ho2, tek-heng7 oe7 kap Siong7-te3 phit-phoe3, kham tit hiong2-siu7 thian-kok e5 hok-khi3, che chiu7-si7 tioh8 eng2-oan2 tim5-lun5 bo5 oah8 e5 ng3-bang7. Kau3 goa2 kui pun2 Seng3-keng thak8 liau2, chiah chai Siong7-te3 lin5-bin2 se3-kan lang5, pi7-pan7 lou7 chin2-kiu3 tak8 lang5 e5 leng5-hun5, hou7 hoan7-na7 sin3 e5 lang5 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3, che chiu7-si7 si2 e5 tiong-kan u7 oah8 e5 ng3-bang7.¡¨ Chit si5 liau2-au7 chit-e5 thak8 chheh lang5 kap i e5 bou2 saN-kap kui-oa2 Kiu3 Chu2, seng5-sim siu2 to7-li2, chit8-si3-lang5 bo5 pian3-oaN7. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit-e5 thak8 chheh lang5 kap i e5 bou2, thang kong2 u7 kap Ki-tok saN-lian5. 
